        "s_word": "affron Soap",
        "s_desc": "Not 'saffron-scented.' Saffron-Infused. We took the threads from our own soil and put the soul of the flower into the bar. You don't smell our saffron. You feel it.",
        "e_word": "ssential Only",
        "e_desc": "We stripped away the Silicon and Triclosan. We kept only what is Essential for your skin to breathe and heal. Zero sulphate. Zero paraben. Zero compromise.",
        "n_word": "atural Herbs",
        "n_desc": "We didn't stop at saffron. We blended it with Natural Herbs to ensure the benefit isn't just on the surface — but deep within. Skin that heals, not just skin that shines.",
        "f_word": "reshness",
        "f_desc": "Because we source directly from the harvest, you feel the Freshness of the farm — not the staleness of a warehouse. From our field to your shower in the shortest time possible.",
        "a_word": "roma",
        "a_desc": "Not a chemical perfume, but the honest, earthy scent of a promise kept. The Aroma of Senfa is the smell of integrity — of a family that refused to cut a single corner.",
        "footer_text": "Most brands give you a name. We give you our word, spelled out in five letters.",
